                    <p>Taux de satisfaction</p>
                    <span class="stat-growth">Stable depuis 2022</span>
                </div>

                <div class="stat-detailed">
                    <div class="stat-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-clock"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>14 jours</h3>
                    <p>Délai moyen de recrutement</p>
                    <span class="stat-growth">-40% vs marché</span>
